Helm is the package manager for Kubernetes. Think of it like apt for Ubuntu or yum for RHEL â€” but for your Kubernetes apps.

With Helm, you can:
 â€¢ Install applications with a single command
 â€¢ Manage complex deployments as reusable packages
 â€¢ Easily upgrade, rollback, and configure your applications

