Helm uses charts â€” preconfigured packages that define a Kubernetes application. A chart includes:
 â€¢ All the Kubernetes manifests needed (Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps, etc.)
 â€¢ Templates that make it customizable for different environments
 â€¢ A values file to override defaults easily

You can use:
 â€¢ Official charts from repositories like Artifact Hub
 â€¢ Custom charts for your in-house applications

