Managing Kubernetes manifests manually can quickly become overwhelming â€” especially with apps that include multiple services, secrets, and config options.

Helm simplifies this by:
 â€¢ Packaging everything together
 â€¢ Supporting versioning
 â€¢ Enabling repeatable deployments
 â€¢ Making upgrades and rollbacks safe and easy

